    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "嘘でしょ……\nこのままじゃ、全然契約取れないで終わる……！！",
      "startTime": 2.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "さすがに受注がほぼゼロなんてことになったら\nミスター・ラムジーからの出資も打ち切られて……",
      "startTime": 11.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "まぁまぁ、まだ開場したばかりですから\nバイヤーの人も、増えてくるのはこれからでしょうし",
      "startTime": 18.0666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3952.4495441999966,
          "startTime": 22.0191162109
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "パンフレットとカタログ、ここに置いときますね\nその方が、お客さんに渡しやすいと思いますので",
      "startTime": 25.0333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ども……それにしても、{user}さん\n意外と冷静ですね……？",
      "startTime": 33.5546714782,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "俺は営業も仕事のうちですから\n今は、うちの事務所もBIG4が何組もいますけど",
      "startTime": 38.2451028824,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "以前は、営業しても梨のつぶてなんてことも\n別にめずらしくはなかったですし",
      "startTime": 45.8451028824,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど。やっぱり一緒に来てもらって良かったです\n次の展示会もお願いしようかしら",
      "startTime": 53.5741722741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それは三枝さんと相談して下さい……と言うか\n日当くらいいただけると助かるんですが",
      "startTime": 60.3784362157,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "えー、業務時間中のことなんですから\nそれこそ三枝さんと相談して下さいよ",
      "startTime": 67.1949205714,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11466.666666699994,
          "startTime": 78.6615872381
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "……にしても、まだ発注は一件だけか\nゼロよりはマシですけど、これじゃ全然……",
      "startTime": 76.0615872381,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6679.999999999993,
          "startTime": 82.7415872381
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、いらっしゃいませ！\nパンフレットをどうぞ……ええと、英語ではなんだっけ",
      "startTime": 81.5451028824,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "……ん？　{user}さん\nその人達、バイヤーじゃないですよ",
      "startTime": 89.1996368406,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "ああもう、英語出来なきゃやっぱダメだわ\nかわって下さい、私が応対します",
      "startTime": 95.0329701739,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（うーん……何か、あまりいい話じゃなさそうだ）\n（俺が応対したせいで、まずいことになったかな……）",
      "startTime": 105.4117695491,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "あいつら、好き勝手言ってくれて\n……今に見てなさいよ",
      "startTime": 113.947054386,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2000,
          "startTime": 115.947054386
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あ、franさん、大丈夫でしたか\n……あの人達、どういう用件だったんですか？",
      "startTime": 119.2451028824,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "要はあいつら、私みたいにミスター・ラムジーから\n出資受けてる、別のブランドの担当者でした",
      "startTime": 126.6524760267,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "『日本のアーティストだかなんだか知らないけど\nファッションの世界では、ただのお子様』",
      "startTime": 133.5520881969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "『日本から出てこなければ、調子に乗っていられたのに\n素人に出資するなんて、社長も馬鹿だね～』だそうで",
      "startTime": 139.7854215303,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "なっ！？　なんなんですか、その物言い\nfranさんの努力も知らないで、勝手なことを言って",
      "startTime": 147.8451028824,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、分かりやすくコケにされたのに\nfranさん、意外と冷静ですね……？",
      "startTime": 155.0451028824,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "だって、めずらしくもなんともない悪口ですし",
      "startTime": 158.1164329209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "今までも、ああいうことは結構言われてましたし\nこういうの日本と変わらないんだなーって感じです",
      "startTime": 165.7497659363,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "私は服飾の専門学校なんかも出てませんし\nモデルのサブビジネスと言うか、お遊び扱いされて",
      "startTime": 173.7830992696,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "こっちは必死でやってんのに\n大半はまともに取り合ってもくれなかったですからね",
      "startTime": 181.2164326029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02-kor017.m4a",
      "text": "だから私も腹立って、実力見せつけてやらなきゃって\nド派手にやろうとして、借金一億……………………あ",
      "startTime": 189.0164326029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_09_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "…………い、一億……！？\nそう言えば更衣室から「借金頭」と聞こえたことが……",
      "startTime": 196.3468833775,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
